  "description": "Farm tractor manufacturing Tier-B actor. Manufacturing-side counterpart of mitsuho operator-side (ADR-2605261015), parallel to sarutahiko↔wadachi (truck) pattern. religious-corp first explicit Right-to-Repair constitutional first-class invariant at firmware level (G10 + N4); combined with tsutae G3 device-level R2R = dual-layer R2R constitutional. Methodology source = YouTube `aSmoLQKdX9E` European farm tractor factory documentary; manufacturing methodology adopted; John Deere-class DRM ECU + dealer-locked diagnostics + patent-locked seed integration + mega-farm consolidation + fossil-fuel-only powertrain + surveillance hardware integration all explicitly rejected per §2(b) + §2(c) + §2(e) + §2(g) + §1.13.",
  "descriptionJa": "農業用トラクター製造 Tier-B actor。mitsuho operator-side (ADR-2605261015) の manufacturing-side 対応 — sarutahiko↔wadachi (truck) と並列 sibling pattern。religious-corp 初の Right-to-Repair 憲法的 first-class invariant を firmware level で確立 (G10 + N4); tsutae G3 device-level R2R と合わせて dual-layer R2R 憲法成立。Methodology source = YouTube `aSmoLQKdX9E` 欧州農機ファクトリードキュメンタリー、製造方法のみ採用、John Deere-class DRM ECU / dealer-locked diagnostics / patent-locked seed integration / mega-farm consolidation / 化石燃料 / surveillance hardware integration は §2(b) + §2(c) + §2(e) + §2(g) + §1.13 で構造的拒否。",
  "methodologySource": {
    "type": "YouTube documentary",
    "id": "aSmoLQKdX9E",
    "title": "Inside Ultra-Modern European Factories Building Massive Farm Tractors From Scratch",
    "subject": "European farm tractor factory (Fendt/AGCO/Claas/Massey Ferguson/Valtra/Deutz-Fahr/Same/Kubota EU/Case IH/New Holland/John Deere EU class) build documentary; frame + powertrain + cab + paint + electrical + drawbar/PTO/3-point test pipeline",
    "adoption": "manufacturing methodology adopted",
    "rejection": "John Deere-class DRM ECU + dealer-locked diagnostics + patent-locked seed integration + mega-farm consolidation + fossil-fuel-only powertrain + surveillance hardware integration all rejected per Charter Rider §2(b) + §2(c) + §2(e) + §2(g) + §1.13"
  },
