      "N4": "Closed ECU / proprietary CAN bus DRM / dealer-locked diagnostics / John Deere-style software lockout — NEVER (§2(b) + §2(e); G9 + G10)",
      "N5": "Patent-locked seed integration (John Deere SeedStar planters DRM-locking seed brand) — NEVER (§2(b) + §2(e); aligns with mitsuho G2 seed sovereignty)",
      "N6": "Fully autonomous tractor SAE J3016 Level 5 (unattended field operation) — NEVER (§1.13 Wellbecoming farmer-land-relationship preservation; wadachi G7 echo)",
      "N7": "Mining / construction tractor (bulldozer derivative / excavator / mining haul) — post-R3 + Council Lv6+ supermajority (tatekata adjacency; kanayama N1 mining echo)",
      "N8": "Fossil-fuel-only powertrain R2+ — NEVER R2+ (G7 fuel sunset; sarutahiko N10 parallel)",
      "N9": "External commercial sale to non-adherent — SBT↔SBT internal carve-out only (ADR-2605192115 §3)",
      "N10": "Pesticide-spraying integrated tractor — NEVER (mitsuho G6 + §2(g))",
      "N11": "Surveillance hardware integration (always-on camera / GPS data sale to seed/chemical company / farm telemetry monetization) — NEVER (§2(c); tsutae G6 echo)",
      "N12": "Cross-jurisdiction mass production / Walmart-style centralized mass-distribution — NEVER (G12 KPI + LANDS.md locality value)"
    }
